# Discord Bot
- Use discord.py (commands.Bot, app_commands)
- Store bot token in DISCORD_TOKEN env var
- Use embeds for alert messages (title, fields, color)

# Binance API
- Use python-binance Client for klines (no API key needed for public data)
- Symbol format: BTCUSDT (no slash)
- 1-min interval: Client.KLINE_INTERVAL_1MINUTE
- Candle array: [open_time, open, high, low, close, volume, close_time, ...]
- Index 2 = High, Index 3 = Low
- Only fetch latest closed candle; no historical scan
